# RealSingles

A modern, elegant dating app targeting discerning users who value authenticity.

## Tech Stack

**Frontend**
- **Web:** Next.js 16.1 (App Router) + React 19.2 + TypeScript 5.9 + Tailwind CSS 4.1
- **Mobile:** Expo 54 (React Native 0.81) + React 19.1 + TypeScript 5.9 for iOS & Android
  - **Target OS:** iOS 26.2.1+ | Android 16+ (latest versions)
  - **Design Systems:** iOS 26 Liquid Glass | Android 16 Material 3 Expressive

**Backend (Shared)**
- **Supabase:** PostgreSQL database + Auth + Storage (supabase-js 2.93)
- **API:** 76+ Next.js API routes (mobile & web both use these)

**Infrastructure**
- **Hosting:** Vercel (web) + App Store/Play Store (mobile)
- **Package Manager:** pnpm 10.28+ (update whenever available)

## MCP Tools

Model Context Protocol servers provide direct integration with external services:

- **Supabase MCP** — Database queries, schema inspection, migrations (**use for all database updates**)
- **Browser MCPs** — Web testing and frontend development
- **Other MCPs** — Vercel MCP, Stripe MCP, LiveKit Docs MCP

## Core Philosophy

1. **Identical functionality, native feel.** Every feature works on all platforms, but each platform uses its native UI patterns.
2. **Single source of truth.** All business logic lives in API endpoints—clients never implement logic locally.
3. **High-quality, native-first code.** Clean, efficient implementations that respect platform conventions.

## Exception

Admin portal is web-only. All user-facing features must exist on all platforms.

